Class OffscreenWindow

java.lang.Object
  vnc.OffscreenWindow
All Implemented Interfaces:
Config, CommonConfig, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, ImageLoader.ImageConsumer, MenuParentInterface, MouseClient, SizeProvider, UniversalConstants, VncEventInterface, VncInterface, VncServiceProvider
Direct Known Subclasses:
HiddenGameWindow, VncAuxWindow, VncDispatcher
public abstract class OffscreenWindow
extends java.lang.Object
implements VncEventInterface, VncInterface, MouseClient, ImageLoader.ImageConsumer, VncServiceProvider, SizeProvider, UniversalConstants, Config, MenuParentInterface

this implements a window backed by a bitmap, but which doesn't touch the regular window system. As such, it's only visible if other real windows, or VNC windows, show it.

Author:
Ddyer
